rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Most of the people living
around here are of races
other than Superbian.

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Part of the reason is that the land is cheap near the
warehouses, but another reason is that it's just easier
to live where there are many fellow Gulan folk.

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0003
rows.name:
But to the Superbians, I
suppose the people living
here can't be trusted.

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0004
rows.name:
If you say you live on the Admar
Wall, people look at you with pity.

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0005
rows.name:
The view here is great, and
there's a sense of openness.

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0006
rows.name:
Well, there is the risk of
falling... but who knows, there
might be something where you land.

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0007
rows.name: I think home is what you make of it.
